<div type="description" n="monument">
<head>Description of Monument</head>
<p>Two <rs type="material">white marble</rs> <rs type="objectType">block</rs>s, of which the right is lost. The left hand block is complete above, below and to the left <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="width">1.30</measure>  × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.93</measure>  × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="depth">0.32</measure>; damaged in the upper left coner, and along its right side.<rs type="objectType">Masonry block</rs>
</p>
</div>
